<p>先生は少し<span class="vocab">風邪<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>風邪</rb><rt>かぜ</rt></ruby>&nbsp;cold</span></span>の<span class="vocab">気味<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>気味</rb><rt>きみ</rt></ruby>&nbsp;a touch of; a trace of</span></span>で、<span class="vocab">座敷<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>座敷</rb><rt>ざしき</rt></ruby>&nbsp;living room; parlor</span></span>へ出るのが<span class="vocab">臆劫<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>臆劫</rb><rt>おっくう</rt></ruby>&nbsp;too much; too taxing</span></span>だといって、私をその<span class="vocab">書斎<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>書斎</rb><rt>しょさい</rt></ruby>&nbsp;study</span></span>に<span class="vocab">通した<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>通</rb><rt>とお</rt></ruby>した&nbsp;had (someone) shown to</span></span>。書斎の<span class="vocab">硝子戸<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>硝子戸</rb><rt>ガラスど</rt></ruby>&nbsp;glass doors</span></span>から<span class="vocab">冬に入って<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>冬</rb><rt>ふゆ</rt></ruby>に<ruby><rb>入</rb><rt>い</rt></ruby>って&nbsp;since the onset of winter</span></span><span class="vocab">稀に<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>稀</rb><rt>まれ</rt></ruby>に&nbsp;rarely; seldom</span></span>見るような<span class="vocab">懐かしい<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>懐</rb><rt>なつ</rt></ruby>かしい&nbsp;longed-for; fondly remembered</span></span><span class="vocab">和らかな<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>和</rb><rt>やわ</rt></ruby>らかな&nbsp;soft; mild</span></span><span class="vocab">日光<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>日光</rb><rt>にっこう</rt></ruby>&nbsp;sunlight</span></span>が<span class="vocab">机掛け<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>机掛</rb><rt>つくえか</rt></ruby>け&nbsp;desktop (covering)</span></span>の<span class="vocab">上<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>上</rb><rt>うえ</rt></ruby>&nbsp;top of</span></span>に<span class="vocab">射して<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>射</rb><rt>さ</rt></ruby>して&nbsp;shine</span></span>いた。先生はこの<span class="vocab">日あたりの好い<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>日</rb><rt>ひ</rt></ruby>あたりの<ruby><rb>好</rb><rt>い</rt></ruby>い&nbsp;sunlit</span></span><span class="vocab">室<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>室</rb><rt>へや</rt></ruby>&nbsp;room</span></span>の中へ<span class="vocab">大きな<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>大</rb><rt>おお</rt></ruby>きな&nbsp;large</span></span><span class="vocab">火鉢<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>火鉢</rb><rt>ひばち</rt></ruby>&nbsp;hibachi; brazier</span></span>を<span class="vocab">置いて<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>置</rb><rt>お</rt></ruby>いて&nbsp;set; place</span></span>、<span class="vocab">五徳<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>五徳</rb><rt>ごとく</rt></ruby>&nbsp;kettle stand</span></span>の上に<span class="vocab">懸けた<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>懸</rb><rt>か</rt></ruby>けた&nbsp;placed; positioned</span></span><span class="vocab">金盥<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>金盥</rb><rt>かなだらい</rt></ruby>&nbsp;metal basin</span></span>から<span class="vocab">立ち上る<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>立</rb><rt>た</rt></ruby>ち<ruby><rb>上</rb><rt>あが</rt></ruby>る&nbsp;rise up (from)</span></span><span class="vocab">湯気<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>湯気</rb><rt>ゆげ</rt></ruby>&nbsp;steam; vapor</span></span>で、<span class="vocab">呼吸<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>呼吸</rb><rt>いき</rt></ruby>&nbsp;breathing</span></span>の<span class="vocab">苦しくなる<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>苦</rb><rt>くる</rt></ruby>しくなる&nbsp;become difficult</span></span>のを<span class="vocab">防いで<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>防</rb><rt>ふせ</rt></ruby>いで&nbsp;prevent; protect against</span></span>いた。</p>

